== Production ==
Vishnuvardhan said he accepted to work in the film "out of inspiration from Rajnikanth".<ref>http://www.sify.com/movies/vishnuvardhan-in-awe-of-rajni-news-kannada-kkfvIhbbeeisi.html</ref>

==Soundtrack==
The music of the film was composed by [[Rajesh Ramanath]]. However, it is to be noted that all the songs in the soundtrack are directly reused from , composer [[A. R. Rahman]]'s  ''[[Muthu (1995 film)|Muthu]]'', the Tamil remake of ''[[Thenmavin Kombath]]''{{'}}s 

